cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.SI 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image retrieval using CNN features. It also involves graph-based methods for ranking, which could place it in the information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The use of manifold ranking and k-NN similarity graph suggests it could also be relevant to multimedia (cs.MM) and signal processing (cs.SI) sub-categories.
